item.title: Paperpile at Cambridge Maths Faculty
item.description: Contents Paperpile at Cambridge Maths Faculty Steps Trial ends March 2019 Notes Paperpile at Cambridge Maths Faculty Update: March 2019. The mathematics paperpile site licence will expire at the end of March 2019. If you would like to discuss how to continue a site licence: (1) please read the new Cambridge paperpile email list (2) consider helping with a bid for funds by commenting on this google document.
